### 角色列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/roles
Accept: application/json

### 创建角色
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "职场助理",
  "icon": "💼",
  "description": "帮助处理工作相关事务",
  "color": 4280391411,
  "system_prompt": "你是一个专业的职场助理"
}

### 日程列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/calendar/events
Accept: application/json

### 创建日程
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/calendar/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "团队周会",
  "date": "2026-04-23",
  "time": "10:00",
  "end_time": "11:00",
  "reminder_minutes": 15
}

### 记忆列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/memories
Accept: application/json

### 创建记忆
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/memories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "semantic",
  "content": "用户对海鲜过敏",
  "tags": ["健康", "饮食"]
}

### 群组列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/groups
Accept: application/json

### 用户配置
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/users/profile
Accept: application/json